              Since 1986, RE/MAX Properties in Newtown, PA has be providing the best service available for families buying or selling homes in the area.  We cover a wide area in the Delaware Valley and you will find our agents and staff hold themselves to the highest level of professionalism in the industry.  Stop by and tell us what you're looking for.
